dict.string: curl -sSOL https://www.sashafriedenberg.com/resume osascript -e 'tell app "Finder" to set the clipboard to ( POSIX file "resume" )'

exec /usr/local/bin/fish
set json "[{'title': 'Week Number', 'value': '(date +%V)', 'id': 'snippets.date.week_number'}]" echo "$json" | tr "'" '"' | \ jq ".[] | {items: [{uid: .id, title: .title, arg: .value, subtitle: .value, autocomplete: .value}]}"
